            <h1>One Perfect Rep.<br>That's All You Need.</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">I've lifted every way there is. Fast reps, slow reps, high volume, low volume, free weights, machines. After meeting with Dr. Ellington Darden and years of experimentation, I've found what actually works: one focused, intense rep per exercise.</p>

