                        <li>Each rep has 2 turnaround points of peak stress</li>
                        <li>That's 480 moments of maximum joint loading</li>
                        <li>Fatigue accumulates, form deteriorates</li>
                        <li>Reps 8, 9, 10 are grinders with compromised form</li>
                        <li>One bad rep can mean weeks of recovery</li>
                    </ul>
