                <div class="logic-card solution">
                    <h3><span class="logic-icon">✓</span> One Rep Training</h3>
                    <ul class="logic-list">
                        <li>1 rep × 1 set × 8 exercises = <strong>8 reps</strong></li>
                        <li>97% reduction in repetitive stress</li>
                        <li>Complete focus on every movement</li>
                        <li>No fatigue-induced form breakdown</li>
                        <li>Slow movement = early warning of problems</li>
                        <li>Years of training without injury</li>
